[0.017617, "o", "\u001b[7D\u001b[21B\r\u001b[1C\u001b[18A\u001b[38;5;246mextend        \u001b[22Cfeinschliff\u001b[2CAdd\u001b[1Ca new layout to the active brand's catalo\u001b[2Cfrom a sc\u001b[1Ceenshot, brief,\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[36C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;246mHTML, or .pptx. Use when extending a brand pack \u2014 in v2 this is a thin wrapper over /comp\u2026\r\u001b[1C\u001b[1Bcontext      \u001b[22CVisua\u001b[1Cize cur\u001b[1Cent context u\u001b[1Cage as\u001b[1Ca colored grid\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;246m/skill-creator                      (skill-creator) Create n\u001b[1Cw skills, modify and improve existing skills\u001b[2Cand measur\u001b[2Cskill\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B                                    \u001b[38;5;246mperfo\u001b[1Cmance. Use when u\u001b[1Cers want to c\u001b[2Cate a\u001b[1Cskill from\u001b[1Cscratch, edit,\u001b[1Cor optimize an exi\u2026\r\u001b[1B/writing-skills                     (sup\u001b[1Crpowers) Use when creating new skills, editing ex\u001b[2Cting skills, or verifying skills\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B                                    \u001b[38;5;246mwork before deployment\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;246m/video                              (imagine) Gen\u001b[1Crate a video from a text prompt using Kling AI. Usage: /video <prompt>\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[36C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;246m[--model <version>] [--high_quality] [--image <path>] [--extend]\r\u001b[1B/speak                              (elevenlabs) Convert text to speech using ElevenLabs and play it. Usage: /speak <text>\r\u001b[1B/using-git-worktrees                (superpowers) Use when starting feature work that needs isolation from current workspace\r\u001b[36C\u001b[1Bor before executing implementation plans - ensures an isolated workspace exists via nativ\u2026\r\u001b[1B/claude-api                         Build, debug, and optimize Claude API / Anthropic SDK apps. Apps built with this skill\r\u001b[36C\u001b[1Bshould include prompt caching. Also handles migrating existing Claude API code between Cl\u2026\r\u001b[1B/memory                             Edit Claude memory files\r\u001b[1B/imagine                            (imagine) Generate an image from a text prompt using AI. Usage: /imagine <prompt>\r\u001b[36C\u001b[1B[--provider replicate|gemini|kling] [--model <model>] [--aspect <ratio>]\u001b[39m\r\r\n\r\n\u001b[7C\u001b[21A"]
